data.description: Come take a look at this four bedroom three bath home in the Luckey Ranch subdivision. This subdivision is outside of the San Antonio city limits in widely growing area! Enter this home through the entry with a mudroom type feature. At the front of the house is the dining room opening up into the spacious kitchen with lots of cabinets and granite counter top space. The kitchen is open to the large living room so everyone can enjoy each other. There are 2 primary bedroom suites, both with full on-suite bathrooms. Perfect for "mother-in-law" quarters, college kid, etc. The third has a built in toy box/reading knook. The fourth bedroom is currently used as an office, but has plenty of room for a full size bed. The backyard buts up to a green belt providing some privacy while enjoying the entertainer's back patio. This house will make a fantastic home for any family while catering to unique needs. Call for a showing TODAY!!!!
